data.value:
To Ben
Please note this program is still pretty glitchy, so here's what does and doesn't work. Works: - Code highlighting for all langauages except PHP for some reason - Opening and saving files - Code folding - Closing new tabs
Doesn't work: - New tabs. Clicking new file makes a new tab, but it puts the textbox from the last tab onto the new one - Cut, Copy, Paste, Delete, and Select all buttons(though you can just do that with your keyboard or right-clicking - Printing - Updates since there's no updates :D
